======================================================================
KEY INSIGHT: dim(Z_1) is constant for tournaments
======================================================================
dim(Omega_1) = n(n-1)/2 (all arcs)
rk(d_1) = n-1 (tournament is strongly connected <=> beta_0=1, always)
dim(Z_1) = n(n-1)/2 - (n-1) = (n-1)(n-2)/2

Since rk(d_2) = dim(Z_1) - beta_1:
  delta(rk d_2) = -delta(beta_1)
Verification: delta(rk d_2) = -delta(beta_1) errors: 0

